
## 🧪 Testing

```bash
# Run tests
pytest tests/

# Coverage report
pytest --cov=app tests/
```

## 🚀 Deployment

```bash
# Docker deployment
docker build -t classforge .
docker run -p 5000:5000 --env-file .env classforge
```

